---
title: Pork Chilli and Rice Burrito Bowl with Tomato Salsa, Creme Fraiche and Cheese
description: This Pork Chilli and Rice Burrito Bowl is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/pork-chilli-and-rice-burrito-bowl-c2cf7ea8-7714ca57.jpg
